 East Asia \n• Exclusive International Franchise from the UK which serves highest quality beef burgers and wild live lobsters imported from Nova Scotia\n• Resorts World Genting's busiest restaurant serving up to 30,000 covers monthly\n• Seating capacity of 168 \n\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\n• Assisting Burger & Lobster's General Manager in managing resort's busiest and most profitable restaurant with service staff\nnumbers of 40 serving up to 30,000 covers monthly \n• Ensuring brand and service standards are strictly maintained as per Burger & Lobster UK requirements\n• Ensuring fast table turnover while maintaining quality of service \n• Performing weekly brand standards training, beverage knowledge training & critical thinking training \n• Conducting monthly mock brand audit as preparation for quarterly brand audit\n\n**************************************************************************************************\nIl Lago Pre-Opening (Italian Trattoria)\n• Assisting the Restaurant Manager in pre-opening responsibilities of the restaurant\n• Acquiring necessary licenses required to run a restaurant  \n• Sourcing and ordering of operating supplies  within OPEX budgeted\n• Creating restaurant SOPs and service sequence \n• Creating beverage menu & restaurant floor plan\n• Interviewing & hiring of service staff \n• Conducting restaurant pre-opening training with newly appointed staff\n• Complying with all ISO document requirements", "experiences/7/jobEndedOn": "2-2018", "experiences/7/jobLocation": "Genting Highlands, Pahang, Malaysia", "experiences/7/jobLocationCountry": "MY", "experiences/7/jobStartedOn": "4-2017", "experiences/7/jobStillWorking": "false", "experiences/7/logo": "https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D560BAQG7nWkm7eojgg/company-logo_400_400/B56Zt9sGTMJYAY-/0/1767340272053/resorts_world_genting_logo?e=1778112000&v=beta&t=RkvyofSRRnDlCqSWI36uHueo_